Five Nights at Freddy's Security Breach is packed full of animatronic terrors, some familiar and others not so familiar. From Glamrock Chica to Monty Gator, from Burntrap to Music Man, this video takes a look at each animatronic, their jumpscares / boss encounters and alternate forms. This is a comprehensive look at all animatronics found within FNAF Security Breach explained.
